performanceLogSummary

Summary
A daily summary of the performance logs. The logs for each day are grouped by name stored with various aggregates such as the min, max, and average durations. Although the individual performance logs are automatically deleted (after a ~week), these daily summary logs are kept indefinitely for long term reporting.
